# Microsoft Intune ‚Äì Hands-on Endpoint Management Portfolio

This repository showcases **hands-on, real-world implementation experience**
with Microsoft Intune across **Windows, Android, and iOS** platforms.

All labs are designed to reflect **enterprise production scenarios**
and are aligned with **MD-102 (Endpoint Administrator)** and modern Zero Trust principles.

---

## üîπ What This Portfolio Demonstrates

- End-to-end **Windows endpoint lifecycle management**
- **Zero-touch provisioning** using Windows Autopilot
- **Conditional Access + Compliance** (Zero Trust enforcement)
- **Android Enterprise BYOD** with Work Profile
- **MAM without enrollment (MAM-WE)** for Android & iOS
- Endpoint security hardening and automation concepts

This is **implementation experience**, not theoretical notes.

---

## üß© Platform Coverage

### ü™ü Windows
- Automatic MDM Enrollment
- Windows Autopilot (User-Driven)
- Enrollment Status Page (ESP)
- Compliance Policies
- Conditional Access
- BitLocker, Defender, ASR
- Proactive Remediation

### ü§ñ Android
- Android Enterprise (Work Profile)
- BYOD Enrollment Restrictions
- Managed Google Play
- Compliance Policies (Root / USB Debugging)
- MAM-WE (App Protection Policies)

### üçé iOS / iPadOS
- BYOD Enrollment
- App Protection Policies (Outlook)
- Selective Wipe & Device Wipe

---

## üß† Design Philosophy

- **Security first, usability second**
- Compliance is a **signal**, not enforcement
- Conditional Access is the **decision engine**
- Always test in **Report-only / Pilot groups**

